  <brief_title>Comparison of Self-Fixating vs Non-Fixating Hernia Mesh</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Study of Self Fixating Mesh Versus Non Fixating Polyester Mesh for Laparoscopic Inguinal Hernia Repair</official_title>
  <sponsors>
